00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:07.276
 Volvorii Timeless - shoes that can change colors. 

00:00:07.784 --> 00:00:09.784
 Sometimes it seems that 

00:00:09.784 --> 00:00:14.214
 modern developers have already been able to translate the craziest ideas 

00:00:14.214 --> 00:00:15.937
 in all areas of our life. 

00:00:15.937 --> 00:00:17.595
 But this is far from the case. 

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:22.834
 Lithuanian company Ishuu Technologies has introduced a new type of footwear for women 

00:00:22.900 --> 00:00:26.093
 which is called Volvorii Timeless. 

00:00:26.100 --> 00:00:29.395
 Today, these shoes are the most "smart", 

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:34.835
 which you have ever seen, and will be able to easily replace several pairs of shoes. 

00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:44.815
 Developers have covered Volvorii Timeless with flexible E-ink displays that allow you to customize color and design. 

00:00:44.900 --> 00:00:48.115
 The shoes themselves are presented in black, white and gray. 

00:00:48.200 --> 00:00:55.075
 The owner of smart shoes can optionally decorate them with additional color and patterned inserts. 

00:00:55.100 --> 00:01:01.615
 But the most interesting thing is that the design of the design of shoes is made using a smartphone via Bluetooth. 

00:01:04.000 --> 00:01:08.000
 In the shoes of the battery is built, which is charged using wireless technology. 

00:01:08.200 --> 00:01:15.734
 Lithuanian developers have opened a fundraising campaign on the Indiegogo website and hope to raise $ 50,000. 

00:01:16.000 --> 00:01:28.396
 For 8 days they managed to get $ 4,000. The preliminary cost of such shoes is $ 149-249 + $ 25 for delivery. 

00:01:28.400 --> 00:01:36.089
 If the company manages to collect the necessary amount, Volvorii Timeless deliveries will begin in December of this year. 

00:01:36.100 --> 00:01:39.115
 In my opinion - these will be great shoes. 

00:01:39.855 --> 00:01:41.855
 Let's see how the girls react to them. 

